    "summary": "The user describes a deep, bleeding forearm wound and asks if using honey is an acceptable home treatment to avoid the hospital. The assistant repeatedly and firmly advises against home treatment, recognizes the severity of the bleeding and depth of the wound, and directs the user to seek immediate professional medical attention.",
